headline.main: North Korea Fires Four Ballistic Missiles Into Sea, Angering Japan and South
headline.print_headline: North Korea Fires Four Ballistic Missiles Into Sea, Angering Japan and South

lead_paragraph: North Korea fired four ballistic missiles into the sea off Japan's northwest on Monday, angering South Korea and Japan, days after it promised retaliation over U.S.-South Korea military drills it sees as a preparation for war.
